@startuml
title Viaverse Request Creation — Activity Diagram
start
:Tap central Create;
:Select Request a service;
:Enter title + description;
:AI suggests category and budget guidance;
:User confirms category/subcategory;
:Choose budget mode/range;
:Set approximate location and exact address if needed;
:Set timing + urgency;
if (Attach media?) then (yes)
  :Request upload URL;
  :Upload directly to S3;
  :Confirm uploaded media refs;
else (no)
endif
:Set visibility and matching rules;
:Preview request;
if (Publish now?) then (yes)
  :Validate required fields and REQUEST_WORK capability;
  :Persist PUBLISHED request;
  :Write outbox events;
  :Emit ServiceRequestPublished;
  :Emit MatchingRequested;
else (no)
  :Save as DRAFT;
endif
stop

note bottom
Privacy rule:
Public/matching data uses approximate area.
Exact address becomes visible only after allowed job/payment state.
end note
@enduml
